{"tid":1514212,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(每晚12點)洗版抗CCTVB大行動，連登仔女assemble！","createTime":"2019-08-28T15:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:49:05.000Z","uid":75759,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"efb73d8c63e57c7867af935cc81777f847824894","tid":1514212,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:52:55.000Z","msg":"是日目標<br />\n1. <strong>黑人牙膏</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DarlieHongKong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDarlieHongKong%2F&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=2e9a6d25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DarlieHongKong/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E8Bq1xB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE8Bq1xB.jpg&h=89d8fa01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>罪狀</strong></span><br />\n除咗落傳統TVC廣告，仲請咗N個TVB藝人做代言，我哋團隊隨便係IG搵都塞得爆個九宮格你話離唔離譜！須知道，啲藝人接呢啲job <span style=\"color: red;\">TVB係會抽佣的，而且食水仲好深吓</span>。黑人咁樣作法根本係直接bum水俾全港最大假新聞宣傳機器CCTVB，我諗唔到有咩理由唔做佢！<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong>雅培</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/abbotthk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2Fabbotthk%2F&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=9f72882a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/abbotthk/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y0hE53N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY0hE53N.png&h=8a37afdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罪狀</span></strong><br />\n雅培一直都係CCTVB大客仔，<span style=\"color: red;\">旗下各種產品都係TVB落過無數咁多廣告</span>，包括雅培怡保康、雅培心美力、雅培保兒加營素等等等等，其中仲要<span style=\"color: red;\">大部分都係長廣告</span>(30s)，最短嘅廣告都播成15s，仲要播放頻率極高，每日浪費樓豬大量時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。而且，根據團隊廣告界手足估算，雅培落TVB嘅廣告費可謂冠絕全部品牌。圖中顯示的數字未必準確，但據手足透露呢啲奶粉公司每年嘅廣告預算係極其誇張，<span style=\"color: red;\">每年最少都有一億</span>，你哋想像吓TVB每年係佢哋度攞到幾多油水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>留言template</strong>，歡迎創意留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n※留言template，二擇其一<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無綫新聞，助紂為虐，恥與為伍，請停止任用TVB藝人作為代言人！希望貴公司重新檢視你所僱用之廣告公司及其廣告計劃。貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手，請於9月4日前回應，否則長期罷買！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我本身好支持你哋公司嘅產品，奈何本人對貴公司請任用賣港媒體TVB藝人作為代言人極為反感，決定罷買產品直至見唔到TVB代言為止。如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司，請於9月4日前回應，否則長期罷買！<br />\n<br />\n好，廢話就講完，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你哋連每日抽兩分鐘時間出嚟洗佢老母臭X版都做唔到，唔好再同我講你要TVB收皮仆街死，因為TVB馬照跑舞照跳，廣告費照收，炒曬全公司黃絲都得呀，洗驚你班得個講嘅連登仔</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08985477a694011daf421f3e091f04f99c2541b4","tid":1514212,"uid":75759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:53:30.000Z","msg":"抵制TVB好Easy，請到以下FB 追蹤TVB廣告，每日更新，恥與為伍！<br />\nLIKE數就是力量，嚇怕廣告客戶<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=8d924ff6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTVB廣告客戶名單: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=fc946c9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a><br />\nTG 抵制廣告行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=cb35ef11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 狙擊活動行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/tvbfucker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftvbfucker&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=e0ef1305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tvbfucker</a><br />\nTG channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/shittytvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fshittytvb&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=cba609f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/shittytvb</a>"},{"pid":"0c85edcfc7a59dd39b387849e04a58d1e244e922","tid":1514212,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17099d148e64124b9b42f435c266a4b565f389b","tid":1514212,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d775983b99130671f32033a578cfbbc536e1f349","tid":1514212,"uid":265902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"無得推都要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e4ebe0420d01590077bb3530e44efa2f6cea99","tid":1514212,"uid":265902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:56:22.000Z","msg":"已留曬言！"},{"pid":"7e38937047f26ec8e54ea827e1b44829df68ba2c","tid":1514212,"uid":265902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:57:05.000Z","msg":"share曬去whatsapp叫人留言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTVB食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5ee9084780539bbd9a8d9f9de5529ff9aadbfb","tid":1514212,"uid":75759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:57:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同場加映</span></strong></span><br />\n【特別宣佈：抵制CCTVB 總攻擊】<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#noTVBchallenge 正式展開！<br />\n呢個諗法早喺7月頭已經有，10月TVB開始同TVB廣告商傾下年合約，接近9月推#noTVBchallenge 係合適嘅時候，有關活動玩法如下：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至少刪除TVB 81-85台其中一台，或者揼爛myTV SUPER，然後影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將相片up上 FB 或 IG，tag三個朋友承接挑戰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用@ tag任何一個TVB廣告客戶 (用@，如果post係public，被tag者將收到通知，請自行判斷私隱風險) <br />\n<br />\n****<br />\n出post Template:<br />\n#noTVBchallenge<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXrZmOw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXrZmOw.jpg&h=c6227fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無綫新聞，出賣港人，抵制TVB廣告客戶！<br />\n<br />\n1. 朋友A<br />\n2. 朋友B<br />\n3. 朋友C<br />\n請接受挑戰！<br />\n<br />\n抵制 @DarlieHongKong<br />\n<br />\n#noTVBchallenge<br />\n#無綫新聞 #出賣港人<br />\n#袁志偉下台<br />\n#黃淑明下台<br />\n#抵制TVB廣告客戶"},{"pid":"2a04c4cee1f8d1a89962ce0502e930f3659a719a","tid":1514212,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:00:33.000Z","msg":"自推十連之一<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗版<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾嬲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷買<br />\n每日任務(3/3)<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b049802e98f60861894b4759328fcaa84c4dff5d","tid":1514212,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:00:50.000Z","msg":"自推十連之二<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗版<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾嬲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷買<br />\n每日任務(3/3)<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b47b83f42ec1bdf89797ace56d60c64d91efd3","tid":1514212,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"自推十連之三<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmo